Title: Create md5sum of a directory
Author: 
Date: Mon, 28 Oct 2013 22:35:19 +0400
Link: http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/Command-line-fu/~3/qvQoupdHyvQ/create-md5sum-of-a-directory

$ find -type f | grep -v "^./.git" | xargs md5sum | md5sum

